msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/alias1"
msgid "player"
msgstr "jugador"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/alias2"
msgid "AI"
msgstr "IA"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/alias3"
msgid "ger"
msgstr "ale"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/date"
msgid "19th-22nd of December, 1942 · Gromoslavka"
msgstr "Del 19 al 22 de diciembre de 1942 · Gromoslavka"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/date2"
msgid "19th of December, 1942"
msgstr "19 de diciembre de 1942"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/date3"
msgid "Dawn..."
msgstr "Amanecer..."

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/date4"
msgid "Early morning, 20th of December."
msgstr "Madrugada, 20 de diciembre."

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/header"
msgid "\"Winter Storm\""
msgstr "\"Tormenta invernal\""

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/location"
msgid "Late evening. Southwest of Gromoslavka"
msgstr "Al anochecer. Al suroeste de Gromoslavka"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/loose_units"
msgid "You lost all your units."
msgstr "Has perdido todas las unidades."

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/loose_village"
msgid "All defensive positions were lost to the enemy"
msgstr "El enemigo ha roto todas tus líneas defensivas"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/name"
msgid "Winter Storm"
msgstr "Tormenta invernal"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/name_big"
msgid "Winter Storm"
msgstr "Tormenta invernal"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/hint/angling"
msgid ""
"angled armor is extremely effective against lower caliber shells. While "
"large calibers have better overmatching, The Panzer III's 50mm shells will "
"have a very hard time penetrating your T-34's armor if you angle it "
"correctly."
msgstr "el blindaje inclinado es muy eficaz a la hora de protegerse de proyectiles de bajo calibre. Aunque los de alto calibre infligen más daño, los proyectiles de 50 mm de los Panzer muy raramente atravesarán el blindaje de tu T-34 si lo inclinas de la forma adecuada."

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/hint/apcr_5"
msgid ""
"Your gun now has APCR rounds. They penetrate much further than regular "
"rounds, but their smaller core deals less damage, they are uncommon, and the "
"accuracy/penetration drop is stronger"
msgstr "Tu cañón ahora dispone de munición APCR. Penetran en mayor medida que los proyectiles convencionales, pero su núcleo inferior inflige menos daño, por lo que son infrecuentes y su precisión o penetración en caída es superior."

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/hint/apcr_6"
msgid ""
"The enemy frontal armor is tough, and APCR shells do not have as much "
"normalization (they struggle against angled armor). This means you should "
"immobilise the target and then reposition for a side shot with APCR."
msgstr "El blindaje frontal del enemigo es resistente y los proyectiles APCR no poseen tanta normalización (raramente atraviesan un blindaje inclinado). Por ende, lo adecuado sería inmovilizar al objetivo y desplazarte para disparar con APCR su parte lateral."

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/hint/at_weaponry"
msgid ""
"Amongst the wealth of weaponry, it is easy to detect Anti-tank troops, since "
"their weapons appear with a red highlight on the 'Unit state icon'. There "
"are a variety of AT weapons, some of which are also useful for anti-"
"personnel."
msgstr "Es fácil distinguir a las tropas antitanque de otro armamento sofisticado por el color rojo que aparece sobre el \"Icono de estado de unidad\" de sus armas. Existe una gran variedad de armas AT, y algunas son útiles contra personas."

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/hint/bison"
msgid "Enemy artillery taking new aim!"
msgstr "¡La artillería enemiga ha cambiado de objetivo!"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/hint/boxes"
msgid ""
"Boxes scattered along the allied territory may contain ammunition and useful "
"resources. You must use these calm moments before the storm to re-fit your "
"soldiers for combat."
msgstr "Las cajas desperdigadas por el territorio aliado pueden contener munición y recursos útiles. Aprovecha la calma que precede a la tempestad para reequipar a tus soldados de cara al combate."

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/hint/mines"
msgid ""
"Vehicles and boxes may contain mines or other defensive equipment. You may "
"drive these vehicles up to the front line to carry all the equipment - but "
"remember to manually switch off the engine, so you will not arouse any "
"suspicion."
msgstr "Los vehículos y cajas pueden contener minas u otro equipamiento defensivo. Puedes trasladarlos a la vanguardia para transportar el equipamiento. Eso sí, no te olvides de apagar el motor de forma manual para no levantar sospechas."

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/hint/pz1f"
msgid "Attention! Unidentified tanks approaching!"
msgstr "¡Atención! ¡Se aproximan tanques no identificados!"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/hint/recon"
msgid ""
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/hint/secret"
msgid ""
"Secret objectives unlock mission segments or open hidden features in every "
"battle. In order to complete them you must scan the map for unusual "
"locations and spend time exploring."
msgstr "Los objetivos secretos desbloquean partes de misiones o funciones ocultas en cada batalla. Para completarlos tienes que escanear el mapa en busca de ubicaciones infrecuentes y explorarlas."

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/hint/shields"
msgid ""
"Every scenario offers unique units. During the hardships of winter battles, "
"it was usual to see skis being used as a platform for a variety of military "
"equipment. You may switch weapons mounted on the shields through their "
"inventory."
msgstr "Cada escenario ofrece unidades únicas. No era extraño ver el uso de esquís en plena batalla invernal para trasladar equipamiento militar. Puedes cambiar el arma que protegen los escudos usando el inventario."

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/hint/skip"
msgid ""
"If you are ready you can skip the defensive preparations by clicking on the "
"right button."
msgstr "Si quieres omitir las preparaciones defensivas haz clic en el botón derecho."

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_narrator/01"
msgid "Artillery barrage!!!"
msgstr "¡¡¡Cortina de fuego!!!"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_narrator/02"
msgid "Coming up right now comrade kommissar!"
msgstr "¡Enseguida, camarada!"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_narrator/03"
msgid "Snow drifting on the horizon! The breeze also brings a distant rumble!"
msgstr "¡La nieve derrapa y la brisa emite un ruido sordo!"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_narrator/04"
msgid "They have... stopped?"
msgstr "¿Han... parado?"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_narrator/06"
msgid ""
"No! Don't be foolish comrade - mine the approaches to our Anti-Aircraft "
"batteries. That is what they're after. If nothing stands between the "
"Luftwaffe and us, Von Manstein will have their troops spectate an aerial "
"massacre!"
msgstr "¡No! Que no te engañen, camarada. Instala minas alrededor de nuestras tropas antiaéreas porque es lo que buscan. Si dejamos que la Luftwaffe tenga el camino libre, ¡las tropas de Von Manstein serán testigos de una masacre aérea!"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_narrator/08"
msgid "They're coming! Dig trenches! Prepare to defend!"
msgstr "¡Ya vienen! ¡Cavad trincheras y preparaos para el ataque!"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_narrator/09"
msgid ""
"The Germans will not risk losing too many tanks - they will advance through "
"the river over tracks of previous vehicles that got across. They will also "
"prioritise any AT-equipment! Try to lure them into a trap!"
msgstr "Los alemanes no van a arriesgar los tanques, tratarán de avanzar por el río siguiendo el rastro de otros vehículos. Además, ¡su prioridad es el equipamiento AT! ¡Tiéndeles una trampa!"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_narrator/11"
msgid ""
"Damn! That means they plan to use it to good effect. Comrades, place "
"dynamite on the airstrip! Something tells me we'd better deny the Germans "
"use of the airfield."
msgstr "Mierda, ¡eso es que quieren sacarle provecho! Camaradas, ¡colocad dinamita en la pista de aterrizaje! Algo me dice que nos conviene evitar que los alemanes utilicen unidades aéreas."

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_narrator/12"
msgid ""
"The artillery is much more accurate than before! This cannot be sustained! "
"Someone must be directing their fire!"
msgstr "La artillería ahora es mucho más precisa que antes, ¡no aguantaremos mucho! ¡Habrá alguien organizando los disparos!"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_narrator/13"
msgid "We're being cut to shreds!"
msgstr "¡Nos están haciendo añicos!"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_narrator/14"
msgid "Sir, the defences further back are not yet ready!"
msgstr "Señor, ¡las defensas traseras no están preparadas!"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_narrator/15"
msgid "Welcome to our Motherland, fascist scum!"
msgstr "¡Bienvenidos a nuestra madre patria, escoria fascista!"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_narrator/16"
msgid "... Yes, comrade!"
msgstr "... ¡Sí, camarada!"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_narrator/17"
msgid "Panzers!"
msgstr "¡Panzer!"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_narrator/18"
msgid ""
"Comrade kommissar, the northern flank has been breached. They blew up the "
"communication lines, sorry if the bad news could not be delivered earlier..."
msgstr "Comisario, han roto el flanco del norte. Volaron las líneas de comunicación. Lamento no haber podido comunicártelo con mayor antelación..."

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_narrator/19"
msgid ""
"My soldiers will work on the barbed wire and inspect the trenches. You take "
"care of the rest comrade!"
msgstr "Mis soldados van a montar el alambre de espino y a examinar las trincheras. ¡Tú ocúpate del resto, camarada!"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_narrator/20"
msgid "Hell! All village perimeters have been lost!!!"
msgstr "¡Peligro! ¡¡¡Hemos perdido los perímetros de la aldea!!!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_narrator/demolition"
msgid "Fire in the hole!"
msgstr "¡A cubierto!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_narrator/"
"detonator_override"
msgid ""
"I've had enough! Germans already know we're here - I'm going to blow that "
"detonator. "
msgstr "¡Ya basta! Los alemanes saben que estamos aquí, voy a activar el detonador. "

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_narrator/p2_02"
msgid ""
"We do not have enough men to cover all the approaches to the village - we "
"will need to reposition with each subsequent wave! The germans will test all "
"our positions!"
msgstr "Nos faltan hombres para cubrir las entradas a la aldea. Necesitaremos rearmarnos tras cada ola, ¡los alemanes van a poner nuestras defensas a prueba!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_narrator/p2_04"
msgid ""
"We've retreated through 10 kilometres already and regrouped by this village "
"- We have had a taste of them already. They know they don't have men to "
"spare, so they advance cautiously with terrible effectiveness. "
msgstr "Ya hemos retrocedido 10 kilómetros y nos hemos reagrupado en el linde de la aldea. Hemos averiguado de qué palo van: saben que no van sobrados en personal militar, por lo que se aproximan con torpeza. "

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_narrator/sec01_02"
msgid "Hmm. Maybe they were the ones directing the fire."
msgstr "Mmm, puede que fueran los organizadores del ataque."

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_officer/01"
msgid "Damn it! Like I thought... they're coming this way!"
msgstr "¡Mierda! Lo que me temía... ¡Vienen por aquí!"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_officer/02"
msgid ""
"Grishenko, where is the bloody mining truck? Are we going to stop a panzer "
"regiment scratching our arses out here?"
msgstr "Grishenko, ¿dónde narices está el camión de minado? ¿Vamos a parar a un ejército de Panzer con la mirada?"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_officer/03"
msgid "Comrades! Listen carefully, we do not have much time......."
msgstr "¡Camaradas! Abrid los oídos, no nos queda mucho tiempo..."

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_officer/04"
msgid ""
"Very Well. Let's go over it again. Surely the germans will try ALL the "
"approaches until they find a weak spot. I think it's our turn next..."
msgstr "Genial. Vamos a repasar. Estoy seguro de que los alemanes realizarán TODA maniobra de aproximación disponible hasta que encuentren un punto débil. Así que nos toca..."

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_officer/05"
msgid ""
"Comrade, take command of the small outpost squad and do your best to "
"withstand the germans. Follow my instructions carefully."
msgstr "Camarada, encárgate de controlar el pequeño escuadrón del puesto y haz todo lo posible por resistir el ataque alemán. Sigue mis instrucciones con atención."

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_officer/06"
msgid "Those swines came very soon. "
msgstr "Poco han tardado en llegar los cerdos. "

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_officer/07"
msgid ""
"They are scouting... Move in for a swift ambush. It would be unwise to "
"reveal all our firepower on such a small group."
msgstr "Están explorando... Prepárate para una emboscada. No sería muy inteligente revelar nuestro poder en un grupo tan pequeño."

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_officer/08"
msgid "Brace yourselves comrades. "
msgstr "Agarraos, camaradas. "

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_officer/09"
msgid "Let's see how those swines like our mines."
msgstr "Veamos cómo se tragan las minas."

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_officer/10"
msgid ""
"This is no time for complacency comrades. The germans will not be gone for "
"long. We must rearm and dig deeper..."
msgstr "Camaradas, en la guerra no existe la piedad. Los alemanes no tardarán mucho en volver, tenemos que rearmarnos y seguir profundizando..."

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_officer/11"
msgid ""
"We put this damaged tank back in action yesterday. Let's see if we can give "
"those bastards a good impression!"
msgstr "Ayer conseguimos reparar el tanque. ¡Vamos a demostrarles a esos desgraciados lo bien que se nos da reparar!"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_officer/12"
msgid ""
"Let some of them go! It may take them more time to come back if they really "
"think we have an armored column with us!"
msgstr "¡Deja huir a unos pocos! ¡Puede que tarden más en volver si de verdad piensan que disponemos de una columna blindada!"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_officer/13"
msgid ""
"I want all reserves to gather around the village. Nightfall is approaching "
"and we have the longest night of our lives ahead!"
msgstr "Quiero que las reservas se reagrupen en torno a la aldea. ¡La noche está al caer y va a ser larga!"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_officer/14"
msgid "Comrades, time is of the essence. "
msgstr "Camaradas, el tiempo es oro. "

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_officer/15"
msgid ""
"The 2nd Guards Army is coming as we speak, we stand here alone until their "
"arrival."
msgstr "La 2.ª Armada de la Guardia se está aproximando en estos instantes. Estaremos solos hasta su llegada."

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_officer/16"
msgid ""
"However, the Germans may be thinking the village is occupied by an entire "
"army. The thick weather has not allowed for aerial reconnaisance from either "
"side. We too do not know what awaits us."
msgstr "Aun así, puede que los alemanes crean que hay un ejército entero ocupando la aldea. La complicada meteorología impide el reconocimiento aéreo. Nosotros tampoco sabemos qué nos depara."

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_officer/17"
msgid ""
"I expect the enemy to attack in full force at dusk. We must do the "
"impossible during the night. Prepare to defend against the fascist scum."
msgstr "Me temo que los enemigos atacarán con todo al anochecer. Tendremos que marcarnos la heroica por la noche. Prepárate para el ataque de la escoria fascista."

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_officer/18"
msgid ""
"I want this village to be the last piece of the Motherland they see before "
"we hammer the last nail in their coffins. Is that clear?"
msgstr "Quiero que esta aldea sea el último fragmento de madre patria que vean antes de que los enviemos a criar malvas. ¿Entendido?"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_officer/19"
msgid ""
"See if you can make some of our damaged units fit for action again. We have "
"several abandoned vehicles around here."
msgstr "A ver si consigues arreglar algunas de nuestras unidades. Hay unos cuantos vehículos abandonados a la redonda."

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_officer/20"
msgid ""
"I want ammunitions distributed and all supply reserves thrown into our front "
"line! You will find them in the awnings."
msgstr "¡Distribuye la munición y manda a los reservas al frente! Los encontrarás bajo los toldos."

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_officer/21"
msgid ""
"We won't take a step back! We won't be leaving Gremoslavka - the fuel that "
"is left can be used to create boobytraps. Blow the barrels when the germans "
"are close!"
msgstr "¡No retrocederemos! No vamos a abandonar Gremoslavka. Podemos usar el combustible que queda para crear trampas explosivas. ¡Explota los barriles en cuanto los alemanes hurguen con el hocico!"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_officer/22"
msgid ""
"There are mines and other tools around the village! Find every piece of "
"useful equipment!"
msgstr "¡Hay minas y otros utensilios en la aldea! ¡Busca algo de equipo que nos pueda servir!"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_officer/23"
msgid ""
"It seems they will attack from the west first. Apparently they want to take "
"the airfield!"
msgstr "Parece que primero nos atacarán por el occidente. ¡Intuyo que quieren dominar el terreno aéreo!"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_officer/24"
msgid "The enemy took the hill by the airfield! "
msgstr "¡El enemigo ha tomado la colina cercana al campo de aviación! "

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_officer/25"
msgid "Fascists are advancing into the village! Hold the line!"
msgstr "¡Los fascistas se están adentrando demasiado en la aldea! ¡Aguantad la posición!"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_officer/26"
msgid ""
"Those pigs are securing positions on the south flank! Don't let them push "
"you out!"
msgstr "¡Los muy cerdos están asegurando posiciones en el flanco sur! ¡Que no avancen!"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_officer/27"
msgid "Their main attack comes from the southwest - Hold on!"
msgstr "Sus ataques más potentes proceden del suroeste, ¡resistid!"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_officer/28"
msgid "Enemy coming from the south! Hold the position!"
msgstr "¡Se acercan enemigos por el sur! ¡Aguantad la compostura!"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_officer/29"
msgid "We have lost the airfield perimeter to the enemy!"
msgstr "¡El enemigo nos ha arrebatado el perímetro del campo aéreo!"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_officer/30"
msgid "The high ground is ours again!"
msgstr "¡La elevación vuelve a ser nuestra!"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_officer/31"
msgid ""
"They have overrun our position at the village entrance! We have to push them "
"out to the other side of the river!"
msgstr "¡Nos han quitado la posición a la entrada de la aldea! ¡Tenemos que sacarlos de ahí y llevarlos al otro lado de la orilla del río!"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_officer/32"
msgid "Yes! The central perimeter is ours again! Make sure it stays that way!"
msgstr "¡Vamos! ¡El perímetro central vuelve a ser nuestro! ¡Que no nos lo vuelvan a quitar!"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_officer/33"
msgid ""
"Damn it! The enemy has driven us out of the southern sector! Counterattack!"
msgstr "¡Maldita sea! ¡Los enemigos no han echado del sector sur! ¡Hora de contraatacar!"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_officer/34"
msgid "The southern flank is ours again! Hold on to it!"
msgstr "¡El flanco sur vuelve a ser nuestro, no os mováis!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_officer/apcr_3"
msgid ""
"Shoot the tracks off! Hit the flat surfaces, don't let them come close!!"
msgstr "¡Dispara a las orugas! Alcanza las superficies planas, ¡¡que no se acerquen!!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_officer/aprc_1"
msgid "Bloody Hell! What on earth are those things?"
msgstr "¡Santo Dios! ¿Qué es eso?"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_officer/ger_defence1"
msgid "What are they up to now??"
msgstr "¿¿Qué planean??"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_officer/ger_defence2"
msgid "It's pointless to stay here! We have to fall back!"
msgstr "¡No tiene sentido quedarse aquí! ¡Retirada!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_officer/ger_defence3"
msgid ""
"The germans advance cautiously. While they move up their forces we will help "
"the regiment finish the village defences."
msgstr "Los alemanes se aproximan lentamente. Mientras avanzan, vamos a ayudar al regimiento a proteger la aldea."

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_officer/gun"
msgid ""
"Comrade, you might want to reposition that AT-gun. The germans will take "
"according measures! I remind you these are not recuits we're dealing with."
msgstr "Camarada, nos convendría trasladar el cañón AT. ¡Los alemanes saben muy bien lo que hacen! Te recuerdo que no son reclutas."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_officer/gun_01"
msgid ""
"Comrades, gather around, we have one more surprise planned for the Germans."
msgstr "Camaradas, juntaos, a los alemanes les espera otra sorpresita."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_officer/gun_02"
msgid "I trust you with the command of our only AT-gun in the sector."
msgstr "Confío nuestro único cañón AT en el sector en tus manos."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_officer/gun_03"
msgid ""
"We have found a great position for it, Comrade, it is on higher ground and "
"out of sight from the road."
msgstr "Hemos avistado una buena posición, camarada. Es en una colina, lejos de la carretera."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_officer/gun_04"
msgid ""
"It is intentionally concealed behind the trees. This is why we have placed "
"land mines amongst the shrubberies. The detonator is ready by the mortar "
"position. Wait until the fascists bring armored vehicles, and then, press "
"the detonator! "
msgstr "Está escondido a propósito detrás de los árboles. Por eso hemos colocado minas terrestres entre los arbustos. El detonador se encuentra junto al mortero, ¡espera a que los fascistas desfilen sus vehículos blindados y púlsalo! "

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_officer/gun_early"
msgid "What was that? You just completely wasted the element of surprise!"
msgstr "¿Qué ha sido eso? ¡Acabas de chafar la sorpresa!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_officer/gun_player"
msgid "Gun's ready! Now let's shred those swines to bits! "
msgstr "¡Armamento listo! ¡Hora de hacerles papilla! "

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_officer/secret1"
msgid ""
"Damn it! We were supposed to keep the fuel from falling into enemy hands. In "
"fact, we should not let them use this airfield at all!! They would be close "
"enough to Stalingrad to overcome our blockade and supply their troops!"
msgstr "¡Maldición! No podemos dejar que el enemigo nos quite el combustible. Es más, ¡¡no deberíamos dejarles ni usar el campo aéreo!! ¡Estarían tan cerca de Stalingrado que podrían romper el bloqueo y reabastecer a sus tropas!"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_player/03"
msgid ""
"Comrade kommissar! What makes you think the germans won't attack in full "
"force!?"
msgstr "¡Comisario! ¡¿Por qué crees que los alemanes no nos van a atacar con todo?!"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_player/05"
msgid ""
"Comrade kommissar, we brought mines with us! Should we mine the roads to the "
"village?"
msgstr "Comisario, ¡traemos minas! ¿Las plantamos en las carreteras que llevan a la aldea?"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_player/07"
msgid "Comrade kommissar - snow dust is visible on the horizon!"
msgstr "Comisario, ¡veo polvo de nieve en el horizonte!"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_player/10"
msgid "They're heading towards the airfield!"
msgstr "¡Se dirigen al campo aéreo!"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_player/apcr_2"
msgid "They... look like tough guys, comrade kommissar!"
msgstr "¡Parecen... tipos duros, comisario!"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_player/apcr_4"
msgid "Right away, comrade kommissar!"
msgstr "¡Enseguida, comisario!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_player/gun_dead"
msgid "Gun out of action!!!"
msgstr "¡¡¡Cañón inoperativo!!!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/narration/rus_player/sec1_01"
msgid "What the hell? Did this truck slip on the ice while evacuating fuel?"
msgstr "¿Qué narices? ¿Se acaba de resbalar el camión este con el hielo al transportar combustible?"

#, boost-format
msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/obj_progress"
msgid "%1% ouf of 3 sectors secured!"
msgstr "¡%1% sector(es) de 3 asegurado(s)!"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/outro_completed"
msgid ""
"Helped by appalling weather and their growing battle experience, the red "
"army held the line at Gromoslavka. The 6th army \n"
"would have to soldier on without help, short of ammunition and food - "
"despite an attempt to supply the pocket \n"
"from the air. The only relief operation came to a standstill at the hands of "
"the 51st army, shattering the false hopes \n"
"of the Germans inside the Stalingrad pocket. In early February 1943, they "
"surrendered."
msgstr "Con ayuda del clima y de su experiencia en combate, el Ejército Rojo resistió en Gromoslavka. La sexta Armada \nsiguió adelante sin ningún tipo de ayuda, escasa en munición y víveres pese al intento por reabastecerse \ndesde el aire. La operación de socorro se estancó en manos de la 51.ª Armada, cortando así cualquier atisbo de esperanza \nalemana de tomar Stalingrado. A comienzos de febrero de 1943, se rindieron."

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/outro_failed"
msgid ""
"The Germans break through to the north as a result of this battle. You "
"should have held the village! Now the Germans can \n"
"break out and save hundreds of thousands of their comrades. The next spring "
"they will be back at the front and \n"
"all hope of a counteroffensive is now lost!"
msgstr "Los alemanes han conseguido llegar al norte. ¡Tendrías que haber defendido la aldea! Ahora podrán \nescapar y salvar miles de vidas aliadas. ¡En primavera volverán a las andadas y evitarán \nque contraataquemos!"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/place"
msgid "2nd Guards Army"
msgstr "2.ª Armada de la Guardia"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/skip"
msgid "Skip defence buildup."
msgstr "Omitir formación defensiva."

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/story"
msgid "The situation at Stalingrad is hopeless for the encircled Germans. They start an offensive from the south to relieve their trapped army. All eyes are now on the 51st Army, which stands between them and Stalingrad."
msgstr "Los alemanes se encuentran totalmente rodeados en Stalingrado. Es por eso que han iniciado una ofensiva al sur para rescatar al ejército atrapado. Ahora el mundo está pendiente de la 51.ª Armada, ue se interpone entre Stalingrado y ellos."

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/task0"
msgid "Hold the checkpoint"
msgstr "Defiende el punto de control"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/task1"
msgid "Hold the village of Gromoslavka"
msgstr "Defiende la aldea de Gromoslavka"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/task1a"
msgid "Gather for the briefing."
msgstr "Reúnete para el informe."

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/task2"
msgid "Drive the gemans out of the village"
msgstr "Expulsa a los alemanes de la aldea"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/task3"
msgid "Keep the AAA operational."
msgstr "Protege el cañón antiaéreo."

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/task_opt1"
msgid ""
"Demolish the foliage when heavy armored vehicles arrive and take control of "
"the gun."
msgstr "Destruye el follaje cuando lleguen los blindados y encárgate del cañón."

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/task_opt2"
msgid "Fortify the positions in the village and prepare for the enemy attack!"
msgstr "¡Asegura las posiciones en la aldea y prepárate para el ataque enemigo!"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/task_sec1"
msgid "Blow up the airstrip to prevent german reinforcements from landing."
msgstr "Estalla la pista de aterrizaje para evitar el aterrizaje de los refuerzos alemanes."

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/task_sec1_hidden"
msgid "Secret objective #1"
msgstr "Objetivo secreto #1"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/task_sec2"
msgid "Board the Bf 109"
msgstr "Aborda el Bf 109"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/task_sec2_hidden"
msgid "Secret objective #2"
msgstr "Objetivo secreto #2"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/timer"
msgid "German arrival imminent!"
msgstr "¡Inminente llegada de las fuerzas alemanas!"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/timer_attack"
msgid "Defend the positions!"
msgstr "¡Defiende tus posiciones!"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1942_12_winterstorm/timer_night"
msgid "Prepare defenses."
msgstr "Prepara las defensas."
